        Who We Are
    

We are a leading global supplier of quality power transmission and motion control products.
Altra Industrial Motion Corp., through its subsidiaries, is a leading global designer, producer and marketer of a wide range of electromechanical power transmission products.Â The Company brings together strong brands covering over 40 product lines with production facilities in eleven countries.Â Altra's leading brands include Ameridrives Couplings, Ameridrives Power Transmission, Bauer Gear Motor, Bibby Turboflex,Â Boston Gear, Delroyd Worm Gear,Â Formsprag Clutch, Guardian Couplings,Â Huco Dynatork,Â Industrial Clutch, Inertia Dynamics,Â Kilian Manufacturing, Lamiflex Couplings, Marland Clutch, Matrix International,Â Nuttall Gear, Stieber Clutch, Svendborg Brakes, TB Wood's Incorporated,Â Twiflex Ltd,Â Warner Electric,Â Warner Linear andÂ Wichita Clutch.
