ALTRA INDUSTRIAL MOTION CORP. (NASDAQ:AIMC) Files An 8-K Results of Operations and Financial ConditionItem 2.02

Results of Operations and Financial Condition

On July 25, 2017, Altra Industrial Motion Corp. (âthe Companyâ) announced certain unaudited financial results for the quarter ended June 30, 2017. A copy of the announcement is attached hereto as Exhibit 99.1, which is incorporated by reference herein. On July 25, 2017, the Company will hold a conference call with investors to discuss unaudited results for the quarter ended June 30, 2017. The chart presentation to be used during the call is attached hereto as Exhibit 99.2 to this report and is incorporated by reference herein.


Item 2.02


Financial Statements and Exhibits


(d) Exhibits


99.1


Press release of Altra Industrial Motion Corp., dated July 25, 2017.


99.2


Charts to be used during the investor conference call on July 25, 2017.




